### 4. Projector Logic (The "Correction")
#### [MODIFY] [live_projector_pane.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/live_controller/presentation/widgets/live_projector_pane.dart)
- **Layout**: Change from `Stack` to `Column` to prevent Title/Lyrics overlap.
  - If Title is 'Top': [Title] -> [Spacer/Expanded Lyrics] -> [Empty].
  - If Title is 'Bottom': [Empty] -> [Spacer/Expanded Lyrics] -> [Title].
- **Scaling Logic**: 
  - Count the number of newline-separated lines in the slide.
  - Set `AutoSizeText.maxLines` to that count.
  - This forces `AutoSizeText` to shrink the font size to fit all lines into the available space *without* wrapping words, maintaining your line structure perfectly.

